sys/concurrent/channels/mpmc.runa
Multi-Producer Multi-Consumer Channels

This module provides multi-producer multi-consumer channel functionality
for concurrent message passing with multiple senders and receivers.
Includes support for work distribution and load balancing.
:End Note

